armors.the_deep_void.harvest_mask.kill: §9-Transforms their soul into a lethal projectile that targets nearby victims and inflicts Hexed III
armors.the_deep_void.harvest_mask.when_a: §7When attacking a foe with Hexed bare-handed:
armors.the_deep_void.onyx.in_darkness1: §9-Attacks get repeated with half the damage
armors.the_deep_void.onyx.in_darkness2: §9-Allows the wearer to see in darkness
armors.the_deep_void.rib_cage.worn3: §9-Teeth won't damage the wearer, teeth trap won't activate and pus sacks won't explode
armors.the_deep_void.rotten_bone.on_key_: §9-Makes the wearer invisible. When in this state, speed is increased. Upon attacking a foe, the effect ends and double damage is dealt.
armors.the_deep_void.soul_voidrium.in_da: §9-Attacks get repeated with a bit more than half the damage
armors.the_deep_void.soul_voidrium.on_ke: §9-Teleports the wearer, damaging the very soul of victims they pass through, applying Hexed I and giving Regeneration I
armors.the_deep_void.soul_wings.on_key_p: §9-Fly vertically rapidly, but with bad horizontal speed
§9-Sneak while flying to fly straight upward with less speed
armors.the_deep_void.void_cloak.on_key_p: §9-Allows the wearer to phase through walls
armors.the_deep_void.voidrium.in_darknes: §9-Attacks get repeated with half the damage
armors.the_deep_void.voidrium_chestplate: §9-The wearer is granted Resistance and Strength
armors.the_deep_void.voidrium_helmet.in_: §9-Allows the wearer to see in darkness
armors.the_deep_void.weaver.descr: §9-Slowly withers away the soul of nearby victims
armors.the_deep_void.weaver_boots.on_gra: §9-Allows the wearer to walk on air if there are no solid blocks underneath
armors.the_deep_void.weaver_boots.on_key: §9-The wearer will dash where they're facing
armors.the_deep_void.weaver_leggings.att: §9-The wearer has a chance to dodge the attack
armors.the_deep_void.weaver_mask.kill: §9-The wearer's health is enhanced until death or until the mask is removed. This has a limit and when reached, the wearer will instead get strength and speed temporarily

item.the_deep_void.all_seeing_sword.desc: §7Right click on an entity to pass your pain onto them, sacrificing your health based on a quarter of your opponent's current health and some durability. §7Each hit makes the sword swing faster
item.the_deep_void.animosity.descr: §7The first hit on an entity deals 2x more damage, 2.5x for players. This resets if the player dies. §7Deals 1.5x more damage to players. §7Hides the name of both the killer and the victim. §7Right clicking will transform the sword into a fake diamond sword
item.the_deep_void.animosity_hidden.desc: §cThis form of Animosity doesn't deal extra damage. §7Right clicking will transform the sword back into Animosity
item.the_deep_void.baby_bone_crawler_neu: Neutral Baby Bone Crawler Spawn Egg
item.the_deep_void.call_upon_the_hive.de: §7Calls upon the Hive to transport you to a safer location
§9Upon right clicking a block while sneaking
§7If the block is a type of bone block, set a destination for transportation
§7If the block below the user is a type of bone block, get transported to the set destination, leaving a swarm of baby bone crawlers behind and blinding pursuers
item.the_deep_void.call_upon_the_hive.to: §7§lThe Hive cannot transport you that far
item.the_deep_void.chained_weaver_spawn_: Chained Weaver Of Souls Spawn Egg
item.the_deep_void.claw_blade.descr: §7Deals more damage to rotting foes, applying one more level of rot each hit. §7Hitting a poisoned foe will spread the poison
item.the_deep_void.cruel_stiletto.descr: §7Sends foes flying, giving speed to the wielder
item.the_deep_void.devourer_shield.descr: §7Brings all foes near the wielder when held up
item.the_deep_void.eye_shield.descr: §7Paralizes every foe in front of the wielder when blocking an attack
item.the_deep_void.eyekin_saddle.descr2: §7Press the Mount Fly key to fly with the Eyekin
item.the_deep_void.eyekin_saddle.descr3: §7Right click on a Eyekin to despawn it
item.the_deep_void.flesh_glove.descr: §7Inflicts Laceration on hit, increasing the damage dealt each hit
item.the_deep_void.forbidden_tome.descr: §7Flings shadow daggers out of your enemies, dealing damage. The daggers then home onto the nearest foe, healing the caster
item.the_deep_void.forgotten_token.descr: §7Locates any Abductor nearby and when under y=0, tells how close the Nightmare is to spawn
item.the_deep_void.giant_bone_crawler_eg: Giant Bone Crawler Egg Spawn Egg
item.the_deep_void.goo_sword.descr: §7Rotting foes get poisoned with Poison II
item.the_deep_void.grim_licker_hook.desc: §7Throw a hook that attacks entities it is attached to
item.the_deep_void.grim_scythe.descr: §7Each hit repeats itself, dealing 6 damage in a AOE and spawning additional XP orbs. §7Killing a foe fuels the scythe with their soul. At 5 souls, right click to throw the scythe. The thrown scythe steals the soul of foes and their lifeforce
item.the_deep_void.hard_flesh_sword.desc: §7Steals the life force of foes, healing the wielder based on the damage dealt divided by 4
item.the_deep_void.heresy.descr: §7Right click to shoot a Blood Shot, a bullet made from blood, which goes in a straight line and pierces. On hit, applies Blood Boil. §7When the chamber is full, the bullet will split into 5 fragment, which are slower, as well as the main bullet. §7When the chamber is full, sneak to fire all 7 bullets at once with higher damage but with less range and pierce. Uses 45% of current health when reloading. §7When the chamber is empty, right click to sacrifice 30% of current health to create new bullets. §7If, when reloading, the shooter has Absorption, Golden Blood Shots will be created instead. They shoot further but with less damage
item.the_deep_void.hexed_doll.descr1: §9-Right click on a Soul Container to summon the Weaver Of Souls
item.the_deep_void.hexed_doll.descr2: §9-Right click on a Soul Forge to summon the Apostle Of Catastrophe, breaking the Soul Forge in the process
item.the_deep_void.judgement.descr: §7Executes entities in front of the wielder if their health is below 25%. §7Right click to teleport dash, dealing damage to foes in the wielder's path. §7Deals half of the damage to nearby foes when swinging the sword at full charge
item.the_deep_void.knife_glove.descr: §7Right click to throw multiple knives, which inflict either Poison II or Rot I, in random directions. §7Right click while sneaking to perform a backward jump
item.the_deep_void.lavendite_shield.desc: §7Flings attackers into the air when blocking
item.the_deep_void.licker_hook.descr4: §7Use the hook if it hits a block
item.the_deep_void.licker_hook.descr6: §7If attached to the hook, retrieve the hook
item.the_deep_void.necronomicon.descr: §7Summons flesh fangs to trap foes. If the flesh fangs kill an entity, the victim will be turned into a devourer
item.the_deep_void.off_hand_void_dagger_: §7Right click with the dagger to attack. Deals more damage after attacking with the dagger in the main-hand. §7Inflicts rot on hit (right click)
item.the_deep_void.onyx_flare_gun.descr2: §7Scare off the Stalker and weaken it on direct hit
item.the_deep_void.onyx_needle.descr2: §7Stab yourself to get the Pain Killer effect
item.the_deep_void.reinforced_pickaxe.de: §7Can crack Bedrock and extract Voidrium Ore
item.the_deep_void.rotten_sickle.descr: §7On each swing of the sickle, dash toward the nearest foe
item.the_deep_void.sentient_chainsaw.des: §7Right click on an entity to saw them, dealing continuous damage that bypasses armor, slowing them down and boiling their blood. §7Right click on a log to break it quickly
item.the_deep_void.shadestorm.descr: §7Fires a flury of arrows that applies Combo to the victim. §7When shot, fire a huge arrow that deals extra damage in a AOE if the target has the effect Combo
item.the_deep_void.smithing_template_gri: §2Enhanced resistance in darkness / Attacks inflict Rot I / Reflects projectiles back at the shooter
item.the_deep_void.smithing_template_rot: §4The user is given Wither when holding a Rotten Item
§9Put in Off Hand and right click to apply the template to modded swords in the Main Hand
item.the_deep_void.soul_cleaver.descr: §7Right click on an entity to pass your pain onto them, sacrificing your health based on a fifth of your opponent's current health. §7Each hit makes the sword swing faster. §7The Painful effect spreads to other targets when the victim dies
item.the_deep_void.stalker_treat.click: §7Deters the Stalker and stops it from coming for a short period of time
item.the_deep_void.stalker_treat.sneak: §7Throws the treat to distract the Stalker
item.the_deep_void.the_harvest.descr: §7Hitting a foe with the scythe will create a soul slash, damaging any mob nearby and giving them the Hexed effect. §7When attacking a foe that has Hexed, one more level will be added as well as two additional seconds.
item.the_deep_void.tombstone.descr: §7A tombstone with a 3 hit combo. When the wielder successfully performs the combo, all mobs around the target including itself will be inflicted with Doom. §7When a victim is Doomed, a tombstone will fall on their head, dealing 16 damage that ignores armor. §7The Tombstone needs to be almost fully charged in order to deal damage
§7Throw a hook that attacks entities it is attached to, applying Hexed to all entities around the hook
§7The hook will attach to the closest entity
item.the_deep_void.void_dagger.descr: §7Puts a second dagger in the wielder's off-hand. §7Inflicts Wither on hit
item.the_deep_void.void_mirror.descr2: §9If in the Deep Void: Teleports you back to the Overworld
item.the_deep_void.void_mirror.descr3: §9If in any other dimension: Teleports you to the Deep Void
item.the_deep_void.voidrium_bulwark.desc: §7Enemies that hit the shield take damage. §7Right click at the right moment to parry an attack, gaining Strength II for a short time and stunning foes
item.the_deep_void.voodoo_doll.descr: §7While using the doll, the souls of victims in front of the user will be slowly drained, damaging them and concentrating them at a point. §7When enough soul is collected, release an explosion at a point, applying Hexed IV to any nearby mobs. §7If the Player stops using the doll when there isn't enough soul, regeneration will be given to the Player depending on how many souls were collected so far

text.the_deep_void.apostle.blessing_line: §cThe flesh is consuming, the soul is transforming.
§cYou.. cannot.. trusted, cannot allow.. to live.
§cA choice is upon us: die by the plague or transform, ''ascend'' into something unrecognizable, something far from human.
§cThis cage has been keeping me together, keeping my mind in one piece.
§cEach passing moment, I feel it slowly slipping away.
§cAnd you, you do not seem affected by this plague.
§cYou have the mark of the void upon you, how strange...
text.the_deep_void.apostle.combat_line2: §cYou deserve only death by my hands!
text.the_deep_void.apostle.hurt1: §cYOU SHALL JOIN OUR BRETHREN BY MY HANDS!
text.the_deep_void.weaver_of_souls.ambie: §c§l§kGOD §c§lA Vessel granted for the unascended... A task failed. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lA Vessel to make one with the Void... Rejected. §c§l§kGOD
text.the_deep_void.weaver_of_souls.bless: §c§l§kGOD §c§lThe plague hasn't reached you yet, God is on your side it seems. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lOur brethren all fell, ascension wasn't successful. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lWhy, God? Why must we suffer? Please, come back to us. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lWill you end it, chosen one? Will you break me free of my curse, of my pain? §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lMy being is no longer of use, the plague couldn't be hold for much longer. Our brethren, now monstrosities because of me. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lPlease, chosen one, free me of these chains, end my suffering, I beg of you! §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lIt shall be my punishment! I shall die by your hands. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lThese chains are keeping my mind sealed, protected from the plague. I'm afraid of what you will see once you free me. Please, forgive me, chosen one. §c§l§kGOD
text.the_deep_void.weaver_of_souls.hurt2: §c§l§kGOD §c§lTo ascend, to make one with the Void.. §c§l§kGOD
text.the_deep_void.weaver_of_souls.norma: §c§l§kGOD §c§lAre you a new desciple? No, you do not accept the Void. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lGluttony goes well with one such as you. You fancy prestigious meals and choose delight over simple bread. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lYou indulge in acts of lust, whether through self arousal or procreation for pleasure. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lA Sinner is what you are. You go against the ideals of humanity and indulge in activities considered immoral. Do not despair, my friend. You may find forgiveness. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lGod is here, guiding his lost lambs to the right path and I shall give his teachings, provide Vessels so that lambs such as you can ascend. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lIf you break the seal binding me to this place, I shall tell you more. I will give you the power you desire... §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lYour soul is tainted, it smells of rot and decay.. §c§l§kGOD

§c§l§kGOD §c§lThe plague hasn't reached you. Are you here for my craft then? Perhaps you are here for answers, for your path to be shown? Are your motivations guided by a twisted interest? maybe you are in search of knowledge? §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lGreed is blinding your actions. You want riches, you want glory. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lSlothful is what you are, you want to be powerful so you do not have to make any effort. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lYou envy others. I can see the look in your eyes, you want my power for yourself, do you ? §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lYour wrath is immense. You look like someone who has seen death countless times. Each of your lives are lead by revenge. §c§l§kGOD
§c§l§kGOD §c§lPride describes you well. You find yourself far more superior to others. §c§l§kGOD
